"8WRGAC08.0A1G" ( + PCB manuf. text and '''1316''' date code) is silkscreened on the bottom of the board in the FCC photos. "WRGAC08" is silkscreened on the top of the board. :The '''Realtek''' 11ac WiSoC used would appear to be RTL8881AQ. :The '''Realtek''' single-stream 11bgn IC would appear to be RTL8188RE.
Default credentials are per the FCC manual. :Default SSID formats may be '''dlink-XXXX''' and '''dlink-XXXX-5GHz'''.
The two power adapters shown in the FCC external photos are... *a '''GLOBAL YEOU DIANN ELECTRIC INDUSTRIAL CO., LTD.''' AMS47-0501000FU (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.2A/15VA -> 5VDC, 1A) *a '''Shenzhen Frecom Electronics Co., Ltd.''' F05W-050100SPAU (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 190mA -> 5VDC, 1A)
